This page just has a summary of all the hymns and their frequency stats, including the new hymns. I will update this page regularly as I collect more data.

## Quick Facts

I currently have data from 24,367 sacrament meetings. If you were to attend that many, it would take roughly 507.6 years---so, more than a couple lifetimes' worth of data. It's also the equivalent of the entire 39-year lifetime of the 1985 hymnal in 13.02 wards. This data comes from 1,248 wards, mostly in the United States. Across all these meetings, there are 83,246 hymns. See [here](/posts/frequency-data) for a detailed breakdown of how this data is distributed across time and space, as well as an explanation of where it call came from.
